                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-87-victim552 t18180218-87-viclabel460"></join>, and live in the <placeName id="t18180218-87-crimeloc461">Edgware-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180218-87-crimeloc461" type="placeName" value="Edgware-road"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180218-87-crimeloc461" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-87-off458 t18180218-87-crimeloc461"></join>. On the 12th of February, as I was passing from my shop door, to the passage, about half-past eight o'clock, I saw the prisoner through the glass door, jump off the railing with a pair of boots in his hand. I called to him he put them under his coat; I ran out and secured him - I took them from him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was looking at them.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18180218-87-verdict462" type="verdictDescription">
